[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "闇に垂れる一筋の糸　手につかみ天を目指す", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "ん……？　私、どうしてこんな所で眠って……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "あれ……このドレスは……？着替えた覚えなんてないのに……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "それにこれは蜘蛛のデザイン？網を張り、獲物を捕らえる生き物なんて……私とは相容れないわね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "みんなの……それどころか、人の気配もないし……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "ここはどこなの……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……まあ、考え込んでいても仕方ないわね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "目の前で起きたことは事実。受け入れるしかないし。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "事実より先の新たな世界を見たいなら、歩くしかない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "この世界は異常だけれど、私は正常。揺らいだりしない。私は私……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "さあ、旅を続けましょう。新たな世界を求めて。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "……ふう。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（かなり歩いたけれど……。　これはどういうことかしら？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（身体がまったく疲れない。　どれだけ歩いても、眠らなくても、　平気みたい……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "（不思議なのはそれだけじゃないわ。　――村にも街にも人がいない。　それどころか動物の1匹だって）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（耳を澄ましても、風の音以外には　何も聞こえない。怖いくらい静か）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（そして最も異様なのは、いつまで　経っても夜が明けないこと）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（静寂と常闇の世界……。　ここは一体……？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "……ふふ。なんだか楽しくなってきちゃった。ああ、胸が躍る！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0086.wav"], "content": "人がいない世界なんて初めて。これこそ、新たな世界だわ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "もっともっとこの世界を旅しないと！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "糸を手にし昇っていく次第に世界が見えてくる", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "其れはどこまでも――", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "――自由だわ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（今の私は、煩わしいと思っていた　何もかもから解き放たれている）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（出会うべき新たなモノたち。　そのすべてに会いにいける）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（この常闇を歩いて行くわ。　さあ、次は何に　出会えるかしら――？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "旅を続ければ、いつかわかるはず。この世界が……一体なんなのか。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110301021, "title": "常闇の世界"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "無数の闇が迫りくる古傷たちが疼く声にならない声をあげる", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "――退屈ね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（いつも賑やかな誰かさんたちも、　お節介なあの子も、ここには　いないから……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "……って、いないから何だっていうの。しっかりしなさいよ、私……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "（前だったら、こんなこと　思わなかったのに……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "誰しも、今の自分を揺るがされるのは、怖いものだよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "でも、その恐怖を乗り越えた先には、新たな自分や世界があると思うよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "また、ここから始めてみないか？きみの旅……自分探しの旅を。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "こんなとき、誰かを思い出すなんて。変わっちゃったのかしら、私……。弱くなった……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "……いいえ、そんなことないわ。私は、ひとりでも歩いていける。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "私は私、なんだから。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"type": "break"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "夢の中？", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "ねえ、新たな世界に出会い続けて、その先に何があるの？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "え……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "新たな世界と出会って、揺るがない強い自分を確かめて……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "確かめるだけで、進歩しない。それで満足なの？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "ゆ、揺るがないのは、強さよ！私は強くいないと……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "それ。くだらない過去と意地につかまってる。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "お父様とお母様が亡くなって、いろんな人に裏切られて、ひとりぼっちになって……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "強くあらねば、生きていけなかった。辛かったわね。悲しかったわね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0034.wav"], "content": "わかったようなこと言わないで！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "全部わかるわよ！私はオデッタなんだから。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "私……？私は……あなた……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0013.wav"], "content": "ええ。だから、あえて言ってあげる。強くなろうとするのは、ただの意地。過去に囚われてるだけ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "私は囚われているの！したたかに自由に生きたいと望む、その願いさえ、囚われの証！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "なのに、否定して……。蜘蛛の巣にかかった獲物みたいに、足掻いちゃって。みっともない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "ちが……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "認めたら楽になれるのよ？……私は弱いって。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "私は強いの……。強くいないと……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "ふふっ、ひとりは淋しいわよね。歩き続けるのは苦しいわよね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "どれだけ旅を続けたところで、どこにも行けない。何者にもなれない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "もう止まっちゃえば――？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "……！？　今のは、夢……？……とんだ悪夢だったわね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "過去になんて、囚われない。両親の死にだって囚われてない。……そう思っていたのに。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "もしかして、私はずっと両親のことを……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（夢の中の私が言っていたことは、　間違ってはいない。だからこそ、　深く突き刺さる……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（突き刺さった言葉から、　黒い感情が染みだして――　私が私じゃなくなってしまいそう）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "こんなの初めて……。これも新たな世界ね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "今まで向き合ってこなかった、難解で不愉快な『私』という新たな世界――。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "退屈しのぎにちょうどよさそうね。さあ、旅を続けましょう。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110301022, "title": "もうひとりの私"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "手にした糸は重みに軋む刻限が迫る――", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "（あれから、ずっと考えてる……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（どんな世界に出会っても、　揺るがない私を確かめたくて、　ずっと旅をしてきた）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（変わらないことこそが強さだと、　そう信じてきたけれど……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "（私が必死に確かめ続けてきた『私の強さ』は、果たして本物？　私は私だけど……私は強いの？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（強さを確かめずにはいられない。　……それは、弱さじゃないの？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0064.wav"], "content": "あ……止まっちゃった……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "……ダメよ、オデッタ。歩かないと。進まないと。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "記憶にも感情にも囚われてはダメ。歩き続けなきゃ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "私は旅人。私は私、なんだから……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "ここは……湖？　綺麗な場所……。今日はここで休むことにして……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……っ!?　だれ!?", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "えっ……!?　あなたは……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120040_story/VO_CHR_120040_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "オデッタ。私の可愛い娘……。父親やっと会えたね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "お父様……？　嘘でしょう……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "オデッタ、どうしたんだい？驚いた顔をして……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120040_story/VO_CHR_120040_STORY_0009.wav"], "content": "ひとりにして悪かったね……。淋しかっただろう？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……っ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120040_story/VO_CHR_120040_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "もうひとりじゃない。強がらなくてもいいんだよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……………………。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（――ずっと嘘をついていた）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（凍てつく夜。賑やかな朝。　綺麗な景色を目にしたとき。　いつも溢れそうになる感情があった）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "（もし家族が、自分を愛してくれる　誰かがここにいたらって……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（時間を経て、自分を誤魔化すのが　うまくなっただけ……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "（私は、囚われたまま――。　だって今、お父様に会えて　こんなにも心溢れるんだもの）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120040_story/VO_CHR_120040_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "もう無理して進むことはない。こっちへおいで、愛しいオデッタ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……………………。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "堕ちるかはたまた召されるか手にした糸は解れゆく――", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110301023, "title": "過去の呼ぶ声"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "見上げる天は光か闇か向き合う地は闇か光か", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……そうだ、オデッタ。もう歩かなくていい……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120040_story/VO_CHR_120040_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "ここで永遠に一緒にいよう。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "歩みを止めて……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120040_story/VO_CHR_120040_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ああ、そうだよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "……そう。じゃあ、お別れね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120040_story/VO_CHR_120040_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "え？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120040_story/VO_CHR_120040_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "ぐっ……何をするんだ、オデッタ!?", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "ごめんなさい、お父様の偽物さん。私、ここでは止まれないの。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "私は自由な旅人。もう、泣くことしかできないお嬢様じゃないから。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0082.wav"], "content": "進むの、自分の足で。私は止まらない！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120040_story/VO_CHR_120040_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "くっ、くく……なんという純然、決然よ！　父親約定された贄の旅路。それを『遺志』で拒むとは！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "父親終着を与えられても尚抗う、高潔な魂。……やはり、闇に還るべき存在！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "旅に終わりはないの。ましてや、『魔獣』に決められた終わりなんてごめんだわ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……旅の途中、耳にしたことがあった。人の夢に巣くい、魂を喰らう魔獣がいるって。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "いつ姿を現すのかと思っていたけど。まさか、お父様に化けてくるなんて。……悪趣味もいいところだわ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120040_story/VO_CHR_120040_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "すべてを見通していた……と。父親流石だ、我が愛娘よ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "気色の悪いお芝居はそこまで。その口、きけないようにしてあげる。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0082.wav"], "content": "いくわよ！　はあああ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "くっ……父親の姿にも関わらず、躊躇いなく攻撃するとは……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "外見なんて関係ないわ。魂を喰らう魔獣なのに、そんなこともわからないの？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0055.wav"], "content": "はああああああああ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "ぐはあっ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "ガアアアアアアアア……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120031_01.png", "speakerName": "魔獣", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "魂のこもった一撃で送ってあげる。喰らいなさい……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0055.wav"], "content": "エンヴォイ・オブ・ジ・エンド！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "グアアアアアアアアアアア！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120031_01.png", "speakerName": "魔獣", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "ふう……。これで夢の世界はおしまい。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "夢なんて、いつまでもみているものじゃないのよね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "新たな世界を見たいなら、歩くしかないんだから……あら？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "白に戻った……。それに……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "常闇が……明けた……？世界に朝が……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "オデッタ！　目を開けてくれ！オデッタ……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "声が聞こえてくる……。さあ、また歩かなくちゃね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "今の私には、帰りを待ってくれる人がいるから。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_02.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}], "id": 110301024, "title": "常闇の終わり"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "オデッタ……オデッタ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0021.wav"], "content": "オデッタさん、気がついたんですね！ああ、よかった……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "ユーディル、クラウ……。私……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0081.wav"], "content": "ずっと眠っていたんですよ、もう何日も。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "ああ。魔獣との戦いで呪いを受けて、それからずっと……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "手を尽くしても、目覚めなくて。本当によかったです……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "そう……。もう大丈夫。心配ないわ。呪いは自分で解いたし。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "自分で解いたって……。一体何を？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "夢の中を旅していたら、性質の悪い冗談をかます魔獣が出てきたから。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "ちょっときつめに懲らしめてあげたってわけ。ふふっ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "夢の中……。精神世界で自らの呪いを解いてしまうなんて……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "なんて精神力なんでしょう。あなたは本当に強い人ですね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……強い、ね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "オデッタ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "……ううん、何でもない。それより、気になることがあるんだけど。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0061.wav"], "content": "テーブルの上に山積みになっている、そのお菓子たちは何かしら？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0060.wav"], "content": "ああ、これですか。ハロウィンのお菓子ですよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "目を覚まさないあなたを心配して、みなさんが置いていって……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "ハロウィン？もうハロウィンの時期なの？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "うん、そうだよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0064.wav"], "content": "それは……本当に長い間、眠ってしまっていたみたいね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "だから言ったでしょう……。でも、これであなたも一緒にハロウィンを楽しめそうですね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0021.wav"], "content": "心配していたみんなも、オデッタがハロウィンを楽しむ姿を見たら安心すると思うな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0028.wav"], "content": "人と群れるのは得意じゃないんだけど。今回ばかりはしょうがないわね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "随分心配かけちゃったみたいだし……。姿をくらましたりせず、参加するわ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "ふふ。さあ、何の仮装にします？快気祝いも兼ねて、どんな衣装でも作りましょう。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "ありがとう。じゃあ、そうね……。黒のドレスを。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "いつもの私とは違う、真っ黒なドレスがいいわ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "それはまた……。いつもと随分印象が変わりそうですね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "どんな私でも、私は私よ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "これから先も。どんな新たな世界に出会ったとしても。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "……そう。自分の内にある弱さに出会ったとしても、ね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "オデッタ？　……もしかして、夢の中で何かあった？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "ふふ、何かあってこその旅よ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "そうかもしれないけど……。きみが辛い目に遭ったのなら……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "大丈夫。それに、私はずっとこれで来たんだから。これでいいの。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "白でも黒でも、私は私。強さも弱さも全部、私のもの。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "あなたらしいですが。あまり無理はしないでくださいね？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "クラウ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ええ、わかってるわ。ハロウィンも、その先も、あなたたちと。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110301_story/VO_CHR_110301_STORY_0068.wav"], "content": "弱ささえも抱えて……目の前のこの世界を歩いていく――。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110301_01.png", "speakerName": "オデッタ", "type": 